Record Class PatientDigest

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.husky.emed.ch.models.common.PatientDigest

@Immutable public record PatientDigest(List<@NonNull QualifiedIdentifier> ids, String givenName, String familyName, @Nullable AdministrativeGender gender, @Nullable LocalDate birthdate) extends Record
Represents the digest of a patient in an Emed document.

Creating these digests is typically done from a CDA-CH-EMED document with the digesters.

Author:
Quentin Ligier
